                    <li>Researched AI/ML applications: LLMs, cybersecurity defense, and forecasting.</li>
                    <li>Assisted with courses: Data Structures, Software Engineering, and DBMS.</li>
                    <li>Built ML models for flood and groundwater prediction (LSTM, GRU, BiLSTM).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Job 3 -->
            <div class="exp-card mb-4">
                <h5 class="fw-semibold text-light">IT Analyst - Intern</h5>
                <p class="text-light mb-1">
                    <strong>
                        <a href="https://transportation.wv.gov/Pages/default.aspx" target="_blank" class="text-warning text-decoration-none">
                            West Virginia Department of Transportation
                        </a>
                    </strong><br />
                    <span class="text-muted">May 2023 – Aug 2023</span><br />
                    Traffic Engineering Division
                </p>
                <ul class="text-light">
                    <li>Automated crash data analysis with C++ and VBA (cut manual effort by 40%).</li>
                    <li>Optimized traffic engineering system operations and provided IT support.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .exp-card {
        background-color: #222831;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.25);
        transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
    }

        .exp-card:hover {
            transform: rotateY(4deg) scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.5);
            z-index: 10;
        }

    body {
        background-color: #121212;
    }

    ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
</style>

